		<p>A million dollars is still extremely cost-prohibitive for a single person. Even with access to a service like MOSIS, having a single, small chip (around 0.9 mm x 0.9 mm) fabricated costs upwards of $25,000 on older manufacturing processes.</p>

		<div class="reply">
		<a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='/?p=1361&#038;replytocom=8454#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("div-comment-8454", "8454", "respond", "1361")'>Reply</a>		</div>
