		<p>Speaking of merging CPU and RAM, you might take a look at the work discussed here:<br />
<a href="https://www.schneier.com/blog/archives/2013/12/friday_squid_bl_403.html#c2821863" rel="nofollow">https://www.schneier.com/blog/archives/2013/12/friday_squid_bl_403.html#c2821863</a></p>

